author: @bunnyvlogs7647
text: I saw this post today in linkled by Steve nouri  Python library to quickly build BI analytics dashboards on top of any data sources with a few lines of code directly from Jupyter notebook. A Python notebook instead of Excel! atoti is great for the last mile of analytics, you can easily slice and dice your data, create and filter interactive charts, pivot tables, and web applications. Run analysis against millions of data points and share the results with peers.   --------------- pip install atoti[jupyterlab] ---------------
